    "description": "<i>An Atomic Game-Engine</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752690/extras/697f66a334b41a7a0b39b0e1add00ff3.poster.avif?t=1634172493\" width=630 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752690/extras/697f66a334b41a7a0b39b0e1add00ff3.webm?t=1634172493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752690/extras/697f66a334b41a7a0b39b0e1add00ff3.mp4?t=1634172493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>  Generate Voxel realms using FATE<br></li><li>  Share FATEs with your friends with links that work in browsers and in game<br></li><li>  Explore curated realms from the DEMOs and Over World.<br></li><li> Each Voxel is an Atom of a system of 256 x 256 !<br></li><li> Procedural generation tools for quick variation and iteration.<br></li><li> Plot atoms using variance and flocking patterns like birds.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752690/extras/0e8a6391fb84cc2dba083607c6e3b587.avif?t=1634172493\" width=240 height=87 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> City Physics - Explore a rainy city block with physics on the rain run off.<br></li><li> Over World - 8 realms clustered around the center pillar.<br></li><li> Aero - Bullet Hell where the bullets are alive.<br></li><li> Star Voyage - Cheesy 90s Intro Space Drama Opener.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752690/extras/866c1fffb26c8bf06a9a4d1e8eb93865.poster.avif?t=1634172493\" width=716 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752690/extras/866c1fffb26c8bf06a9a4d1e8eb93865.webm?t=1634172493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752690/extras/866c1fffb26c8bf06a9a4d1e8eb93865.mp4?t=1634172493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752690/extras/f19646e0d81d4a4b89c366223faaa924.avif?t=1634172493\" width=188 height=83 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Use the Weave or LISP editors bidirectionally.<br></li><li> a Timeline that orchestrates events across a song's duration<br></li><li> .vox support for plotting complex voxels<br></li><li> Drag and Drop assets onto the browser to mix in<br></li><li> Download any part of a FATE file as its original form (VOX/LISP/MP3)</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752690/extras/a76354e2f972f338dc448ef250e22be9.poster.avif?t=1634172493\" width=740 height=566 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752690/extras/a76354e2f972f338dc448ef250e22be9.webm?t=1634172493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752690/extras/a76354e2f972f338dc448ef250e22be9.mp4?t=1634172493\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752690/extras/bffbfb2c2545a054f38d82ede3299ab7.poster.avif?t=1634172493\" width=538 height=566 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752690/extras/bffbfb2c2545a054f38d82ede3299ab7.webm?t=1634172493\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1752690/ex